xtense, complex just like wordpress. Oh wait the guys who created woocommerce are the ones who create wordpress. Makes sense</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Featureless without costly $$$$ addons</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jak0works\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1c788a928abe467a1d8db20d3cdf7733?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1c788a928abe467a1d8db20d3cdf7733?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jak0works\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jak0works</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 24, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Featureless without costly $$$$ addons. Everything you would require to do basic business is an expensive subscription $$$$ addon. \n\n	<li>Example $79 per year just to bulk update prices. \nAdding Coupon Campaigns is $49 per year. \nCustomizable shipping options will set you back another $99 per year!</li>\n\n\nGreed!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great e-commerce</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<di