r/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=2234716\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/the-events-calendar/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=2234716\" alt=\"CSV Importer\"></a><p>CSV Importer</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:15099:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Used to be great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tcmacadmind\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9111a7e424a7951a8cf0a4555cee59f8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9111a7e424a7951a8cf0a4555cee59f8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tcmacadmind\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tcmacadmind</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 30, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">You have TOTALLY stuffed this plugin. It used to be great but now it is awful. We can no longer have multiple RSVP\'s as we could before. We do not \"sell: tickets so don\'t use that side of the events plugin at all but we have a need for RSVP\'s for people attending and also RSVP\'s for people wishing to camp on site, we used to be able to do this but after the latest updates we can only have 1 RSVP per event. This now has made the whole calendar useless as it doesn\'t cater for our needs, pity because I loved the earlier version, don\'t know why it had to be changed.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">This plugin doesn&#039;t work at all</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sociali1\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9927464a101aa682dbd00baee6b4c540?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9927464a101aa682dbd00baee6b4c540?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sociali1\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sociali1</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 25, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Suddenly this plugin just doesn\'t work. When I wanted to create an event page, when the page was finished and I started going to the online view, it turned out that the page was not found. There is only a 404 Page Error page. Whereas previously it was normal, and I had absolutely nothing to change.\n\nI thought it would take a while, but it still doesn\'t work. And some of the events pages that I created, all disappeared, couldn\'t be found anymore. Every time I create the event page, it always gets an error, what I have made is erased again. Please repair the damage immediately, because it is very necessary. And please respond</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Not as Out of Box as One Would Think</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ikrmedia\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b0a94e0b741af4dae796f5810d84e0ad?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b0a94e0b741af4dae796f5810d84e0ad?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ikrmedia\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ikrmedia</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 24, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">First of all, you can tell a lot of hard work went/goes into this platform.\n\nThat being said, I think it\'s pretty basic as far as it\'s design goes and the output relies heavily on you implementing your own CSS (which is fine but the out of box pitch becomes deceiving). \n\nThe customizer settings only offer a few options and even that doesn\'t update the colors. Still had to add my own CSS which still doesn\'t fix everything. Even simple calendar button colors. \n\nSupport is helpful but no resolve. The technicians CSS didn\'t work either and then they just send me links to their support docs letting me know that I can implement my own CSS.\n\nWe use Astra (Pro) and Elementor (Pro) with just about every application. Maybe we need to use a different theme? We\'ve tried on two other themes and still face the same hurdles.\n\nFor the price of all the plugins I think it\'s more efficient to just use MeetUp and integrate that into your website. Unless you or you have a developer for custom CSS...\n\nHave a clean install with styling you\'d like to share? I\'d love to see it!\n\nThanks!\n\nJake</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/manuelguns\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b630e439a0eb5e3b281b3008f247796f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b630e439a0eb5e3b281b3008f247796f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/manuelguns\" class=\"reviewer-name\">manuelguns</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 24, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very good</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great calendar plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quintawine\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/88ece1fc079f80e1d019956985efa4d4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/88ece1fc079f80e1d019956985efa4d4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quintawine\" class=\"reviewer-name\">quintawine</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 19, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works really well end fantastic support</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">bon produit</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marc1955\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar