easilo.wordpress.com/\">Takayuki Miyoshi</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:43:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:12:\"takayukister\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:43:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bb7bc21850c77e9eb16b44102f4a539d?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Takayuki Miyoshi\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"5.5\";s:6:\"tested\";s:3:\"5.7\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:6:\"rating\";i:82;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:1307;i:4;i:132;i:3;i:59;i:2;i:50;i:1;i:330;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:1878;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:770;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:216;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:5000000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2021-02-24 12:24pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2007-08-02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:25:\"https://contactform7.com/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:2974:\"<p>Contact Form 7 can manage multiple contact forms, plus you can customize the form and the mail contents flexibly with simple markup. The form supports Ajax-powered submitting, CAPTCHA, Akismet spam filtering and so on.</p>\n<h4>Docs and support</h4>\n<p>You can find <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">docs</a>, <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a> and more detailed information about Contact Form 7 on <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contactform7.com</a>. When you can&#8217;t find the answer to your question on the FAQ or in any of the documentation, check the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\">support forum</a> on WordPress.org. If you can&#8217;t locate any topics that pertain to your particular issue, post a new topic for it.</p>\n<h4>Contact Form 7 needs your support</h4>\n<p>It is hard to continue development and support for this free plugin without contributions from users like you. If you enjoy using Contact Form 7 and find it useful, please consider <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/donate/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">making a donation</a>. Your donation will help encourage and support the plugin&#8217;s continued development and better user support.</p>\n<h4>Privacy notices</h4>\n<p>With the default configuration, this plugin, in itself, does not:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>track users by stealth;</li>\n<li>write any user personal data to the database;</li>\n<li>send any data to external servers;</li>\n<li>use cookies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you activate certain features in this plugin, the contact form submitter&#8217;s personal data, including their IP address, may be sent to the service provider. Thus, confirming the provider&#8217;s privacy policy is recommended. These features include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA (<a href=\"https://policies.google.com/?hl=en\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google</a>)</li>\n<li>Akismet (<a href=\"https://automattic.com/privacy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Automattic</a>)</li>\n<li>Constant Contact (<a href=\"https://www.endurance.com/privacy\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Endurance International Group</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sendinblue.com/legal/privacypolicy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Sendinblue</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Recommended plugins</h4>\n<p>The following plugins are recommended for Contact Form 7 users:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/flamingo/\">Flamingo</a> by Takayuki Miyoshi &#8211; With Flamingo, you can save submitted messages via contact forms in the database.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bogo/\">Bogo</a> by Takayuki Miyoshi &#8211; Bogo is a straight-forward multilingual plugin that doesn&#8217;t cause headaches.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Translations</h4>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/translating-contact-form-7/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">translate Contact Form 7</a> on <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/contact-form-7\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">translate.wordpress.org</a>.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:458:\"<ol>\n<li>Upload the entire <code>contact-form-7</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the <strong>Plugins</strong> screen (<strong>Plugins &gt; Installed Plugins</strong>).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You will find <strong>Contact</strong> menu in your WordPress admin screen.</p>\n<p>For basic usage, have a look at the <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">plugin&#8217;s website</a>.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:439:\"<p>Do you have questions or issues with Contact Form 7? Use these support channels appropriately.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Docs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\">Support forum</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/support/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Support</a></p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:184:\"<p>For more information, see <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/category/releases/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Releases</a>.</p>\n<h4>5.4</h4>\n<p>https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-54/</p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:225:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\" alt=\"screenshot-1.png\"></a><p>screenshot-1.png</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14580:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">5.4の不具合</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dgb1japan\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1154f47f42e8158e689af0f7fc491ee?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1154f47f42e8158e689af0f7fc491ee?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dgb1japan\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dgb1japan</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 30, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">他の人のレビューの通り、Ver.5.4で不具合が生じているようです。\n一つ前バージョンに戻したら、正常にメッセージが送信できるようになりましたが、5.4では、送信ボタンを押したあと、何も変化がありません。\n\nプラグインの干渉も考えましたが、バージョン戻しただけで問題が解決したので、原因は5.4アップデートのよう考えています。\n　\nとても良いプラグインで、昔から使っているので、なかなか他のモノを使う気にはなれません。\nしばらく、前バージョンで使わせていただこうと思います。</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">After the latest update i am getting into issues.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shujashah\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0df3f836c239de36c110a315f241daf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0df3f836c239de36c110a315f241daf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shujashah\" class=\"reviewer-name\">shujashah</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 27, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hi after updating to 5.4, i am not able to fill the contact form as it is referred as spam...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">WTF? Plugin has stopped working!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pashkaru\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b79af17e6d7199289c5abac72e8d7f8e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b79af17e6d7199289c5abac72e8d7f8e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pashkaru\" class=\"reviewer-name\">PashkaRu</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 26, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">What happened? The plugin throws errors and does not send messages! Do something about it urgently!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">v5.4 breaks eventually with cache plugins -- downgrade to 5.3.2 or remove</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/1seth\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/585856073a7f8720c59589cb23bfd10a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/585856073a7f8720c59589cb23bfd10a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/1seth\" class=\"reviewer-name\">1seth</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 25, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Plenty of threads in the support about this.\n\nnonce code breaking eventually for those with cache plugins. Was working fine before 5.4.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Latest update broke site -- no word on fix.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/venya\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f94102395dfe66f7fbba551b043ff656?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f94102395dfe66f7fbba551b043ff656?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/venya\" class=\"reviewer-name\">venya</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 21, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Version 5.4 broke the site\'s contact form. No confirmation messege, and people would hit submit over and over again, sending multiple copies of the message. Lots of folks leaving negative comments. Developer should acknowledge issue.  Rollback to previous version fixed problems. \n </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very simple and furiously efficient</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vinzou\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dfedde2ad63278209505cc7cb43c4987?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dfedde2ad63278209505cc7cb43c4987?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vinzou\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Vinzou <small>(vinzou)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 20, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">the right plugin for everybody</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Developer doesnt care about updates</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/converted\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40c4b0770052cd75cedc6207c58d028d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/40c4b0770052cd75cedc6207c58d028d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/converted\" class=\"reviewer-name\">converted</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 18, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s been 2 weeks and the latest version 5.4 is still buggy and not working. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Contact Form Not Working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jackslobodian\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8568f715acd86c5228f4dbc86330db62?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8568f715acd86c5228f4dbc86330db62?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jackslobodian\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jackslobodian</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 18, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have had the contact form on my website since 2019 and not really touched it seen. I just tried to run a test and send myself a email from a seperate email address and I am receiving this message \'There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\' </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">simplicity in the perfection or should it be the other way around</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fightingships\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2293805fc7d51752e97cd6980ed6c386?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2293805fc7d51752e97cd6980ed6c386?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fightingships\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fightingships</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 14, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s the ideal little form builder for a normal blog / website and it\'s exceptionally easy to use.  The free version is more than sufficient for most needs. It\'s stable. Well thought out. What else can you be asking for?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">скорость</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexkazachok\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a22247b172b0d326426649d8a10bae53?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a22247b172b0d326426649d8a10bae53?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' 