r-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[40077083d72188c6da0]\" data-title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Services\" title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Services\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"570\" alt=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Services\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-852610\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices-200x60.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices-400x120.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices-600x180.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices-800x240.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices-1200x360.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-availableservices.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-184\"><p>This section pretty straightforward and easy to replicate. It starts with a <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Container</a>. A single (1/1 &#8211; 100%) width <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Column</a> is added to the container, which displays a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>.</p>\n<p>Below the 100% width Column is a single row of four (1/4 &#8211; 25%) Columns, each with Title and <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>. Some useful functionality to highlight:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-41\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas\" style=\"color:#f86635;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><strong>Element Visibility</strong> &#8211; You can choose to show or hide a Container, column, or Element on small, medium, or large screens, and you can select more than one at a time. Each of the three sizes has a custom width setting on the Avada Builder Elements tab in the Global Options. Read more <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/options/the-avada-visibility-system/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas\" style=\"color:#f86635;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><strong>Responsive Styling</strong> &#8211; You can set specific styling options independently for different screen sizes. Responsive styling allows you to control settings that correspond to three dimensions, Large (Desktop), Medium (Tablet), and Small (Phone). Read more <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/options/responsive-option-sets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas\" style=\"color:#f86635;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\"><strong>Flexbox</strong> &#8211; Flexbox is a CSS3 layout model that provides a more efficient way to design, align and distribute space for Columns inside of any Container. Read more <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/options/introducing-flexbox-for-containers-and-columns/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-232{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-232{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-232 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">More Information &#8211; CTA</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-93 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[19a37fd53a6ed571f54]\" data-title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Info CTA\" title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Info CTA\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"863\" alt=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Info CTA\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-852611\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1-200x91.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1-400x182.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1-600x273.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1-800x363.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1-1200x545.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-infocta1.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-185\"><p>A Call-to-action (CTA) is a marketing method designed to prompt an immediate response or encourage a direct sale from your website visitors. There is no hard and fast rule about how you should create them, other than being an attraction and conversion point on your website. Using the Avada Design Elements, you can make any CTA style that you feel will work for your online business.</p>\n<p>For this example, the CTA section is made up of two (1/2 – 50%) Columns side by side. An <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Image Element</a> is added to the left Column. In the right Column you will see couple of <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element&#8217;s</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Button Element</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-233{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-233{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-233 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">CTA &#8211; Call to Action</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-94 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[3e908c37deabd92b20d]\" data-title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Main CTA\" title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Main CTA\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Main CTA\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-852612\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta-200x56.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta-400x112.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta-600x169.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta-800x225.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta-1200x337.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-maincta.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-186\"><p>A standard Call-to-action (CTA) is illustrated below and is set up with a (1/1 &#8211; 100%) <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Column</a>, a couple of <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element&#8217;s</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Button Element</a>.</p>\n<p>Depending on the marketing goal, CTA&#8217;s can drive a variety of different actions and results for your website visitors. Check this article for some CTA inspiration, <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/call-to-action-examples\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">39 Call-to-Action Examples You Can&#8217;t Help But Click</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-234{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-234{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-234 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Nested Columns</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-95 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[017a61d7015c1c22127]\" data-title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns\" title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"496\" alt=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Nested Columns\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-852613\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1-200x52.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1-400x104.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1-600x157.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1-800x209.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1-1200x313.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-nestedcolumns1.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-187\"><p>This section uses the versatile <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nested Column Element</a>, and simply put are Columns within Columns. For example, you can add two 1/4 (25% width) Columns inside a 1/2 (50% width) Column; This will mean that the Nested Columns will be 1/4 width of the 1/2 Column and a total of 1/8 (12,5%) of the entire page width.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-235{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-235{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-235 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Amazing Brands</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-96 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[f53b17ca335bfa71739]\" data-title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Brands\" title=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Brands\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"245\" alt=\"Avada Virtual Assistant Brands\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-852614\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands-200x26.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands-400x52.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands-600x77.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands-800x103.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands-1200x155.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/avada-virtual-assistant-brands.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-188\"><p>This section does well to highlight client partnerships or repurposed to showcase information related to your services and products, and more. Right now, the setup is single full width (1/1 &#8211; 100%) Column with a Title Element. Below is a single row of five (1/5 &#8211; 20%) Columns, each with an Image Element.</p>\n<p>As an alternative, an <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-carousel-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Image Carousel Element</a> can be used for a similar visual effect.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-236{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-236{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margi