dding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-48 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start\" style=\"max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-59 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-263{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-263{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-263 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"homepage\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Exploring The Homepage Layout</h2></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-264{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-264{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-264 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">The Header</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-210\"><p>For the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Handmade</a> prebuilt website, the Header was created using the Avada <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-header-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Header Builder</a> and is set globally across the website. This means that every page and post will use the same Header layout without any further conditions set. For example, you can change this if required by creating a unique Header layout for different pages or posts. You can check how this is structured on the backend by clicking this <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/handmade-header-backend.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rel=\"iLightbox\">link</a>.</p>\n</div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-104 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[af4188914c5ea08038c]\" data-title=\"Handmade header\" title=\"Handmade header\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"172\" alt=\"Handmade Header\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840629\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-200x18.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-400x36.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-600x54.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-800x72.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice-1200x109.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-header-slice.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-265{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-265{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-265 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">The Page Content</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-211\"><p>The content part of the homepage, the area between the Header and Footer, does not use a page title bar. You can change this page&#8217;s content in an infinite number of ways to best suit your business marketing and brand requirements.</p>\n<p>Page and Post content is structured using Container and Column Elements, and if required, Nested Columns. Check out the help file links below for detailed information and videos explaining what they are and how to use them:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-47\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas\" style=\"color:#bc4b20;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">What are Containers, and how to use them? Read more <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas\" style=\"color:#bc4b20;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">What are Columns, and how to use them? Read more <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-info-circle fas\" style=\"color:#bc4b20;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">What are Nested Columns, and how to use them? Read more <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</div></li></ul></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-59{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-59 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-59{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-59 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-59{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-59 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-48{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-49 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start\" style=\"max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-60 fusion-flex-column\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-266{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-266{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-266 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">The Hero</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-105 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[7017c3da32d92254b05]\" data-title=\"Handmade Hero Section\" title=\"Handmade Hero Section\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"576\" alt=\"Handmade Hero Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840637\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-200x61.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-400x121.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-600x182.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-800x243.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice-1200x364.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-hero-slice.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-212\"><p>Instead of using a traditional image slider, like the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Slider</a> or <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-third-party-integration/slider-revolution/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Slider Revolution</a>, as the above-the-fold hero section, this prebuilt site uses a <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Container</a>. Added to that are three (1/3 &#8211; 33%) width <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Columns</a> and a <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/nested-columns-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nested Column</a> within each Column.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-267{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-267{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-267 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Content Boxes</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-106 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[48af49297d213550329]\" data-title=\"Content Boxes\" title=\"Content Boxes\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"202\" alt=\"Content Boxes\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840647\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-200x21.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-400x43.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-600x64.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-800x85.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice-1200x128.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-boxes-slice.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-213\"><p>The <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/content-boxes-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Content Box Element</a> is a handy and flexible Element with a wide range of styling options that you can use in so many different ways. In this instance, they display value points for potential product buyers and can be changed to best your website&#8217;s messaging.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-268{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-268{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-268 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">CTA &#8211; Call to Action</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-107 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[9762437275d0cc0cffa]\" data-title=\"Call to Action\" title=\"Call to Action\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"267\" alt=\"Call to Action\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840652\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-200x28.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-400x56.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-600x84.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-800x112.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice-1200x169.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-cta-slice.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-214\"><p>A Call-to-action (CTA) is a marketing method designed to prompt an immediate response or encourage a direct sale from your website visitors. There is no hard and fast rule about how you should create them, other than being an attraction and conversion point on your website. Using the Avada Design Elements, you can make any CTA style that you feel will work for your online business.</p>\n<p>For this example, the CTA section is made up of a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Button Element</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-269{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-269{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-269 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Popular Categories</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-108 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[4d986982cd842dea34d]\" data-title=\"Popular Categories\" title=\"Popular Categories\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"433\" alt=\"Popular Categories\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840663\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-200x46.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-400x91.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-600x137.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-800x182.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice-1200x273.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-popularcats-slice.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-215\"><p>There are various ways to display popular product categories, using WooCommerce or, as in this instance, a series of four columns is used to direct the website visitor. Assigned to each <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/column-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Column Element</a> is an <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Image Element</a> and then below that, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>.</p>\n<p>The final point to highlight is that each of the four columns is a clickable area by enabling the <strong>Link URL</strong> option within the Column Element settings.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-270{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-270{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-270 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"subscriptionform\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Subscription Form</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-109 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[9d4e2e9e1143b9f777b]\" data-title=\"Subscription Form\" title=\"Subscription Form\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"230\" alt=\"Subscription Form\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840668\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-200x24.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-400x48.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-600x73.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-800x97.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice-1200x145.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/handmade-homepage-subscribe-slice.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-216\"><p>The <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-form-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Form Builder</a> is used to design and build this subscription form. The Form Builder is very flexible and allows you to create many types of forms that you can use on your <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NhBSeq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> website. For any form that you create, you can add them to a page or post as a single instance or you can set the form to display <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/forms/avada-forms-global-options/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">globally</a> across the website, which then allows you to manage one form. If a form is showing on all pages, for example, and you edit the form, the same changes show across all form instances.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-271{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-271{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-271 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Editor&#8217;s Pick</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-110 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[6b27f1ff8dd4fb71ef3]\" data-title=\"Editor&#8217;s Pick\" title=\"Editor&#8217;s Pick\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"936\" alt=\"Editor&#039;s Pick\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850288\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-200x99.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-400x197.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-600x296.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-800x394.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section-1200x591.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/editors-pick-section.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-217\"><p>This section is relatively straight forward. It starts off with a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and then a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/woo-shortcodes-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce Shortcode Element</a> to display the products in two rows of five. The parameters for the WooCommerce Shortcode Element are as follows:</p>\n</div>[recent_products limit=\"10\" columns=\"5\" orderby=\"rand\" order=\"desc\"]<div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-272{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-272{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-272 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Product CTA&#8217;s</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-111 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[1e6e894c98c5e644e0b]\" data-title=\"Product CTA&#8217;s\" title=\"Product CTA&#8217;s\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"934\" alt=\"Product CTA&#039;s\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850292\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-200x98.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-400x197.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-600x295.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-800x393.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas-1200x590.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/product-ctas.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-218\"><p>As shown in the image above, two Containers are added to the page content to advertize segmented product lines. The first <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/elements/container-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Container Element</a> has a 2/3 Column and a 1/1 Column below that. The 2/3 Column houses two <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Elements</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a> for come text, and a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Button Element</a>. The 1/1 Column has a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/section-separator-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Section Separator Element</a> using the paper style option for an enhanced visual effect.</p>\n<p>The second Container Element has 6 Columns added, and to each, we have added an <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/image-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Image Element</a> and then below that, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>.</p>\n<p>The final point to highlight is that each of the six columns is a clickable area by enabling the <strong>Link URL</strong> option within the Column Element settings.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-273{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-273{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-273 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Holiday Decorations</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-112 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[f7ea8bc600b3ed82adb]\" data-title=\"Holiday Decorations\" title=\"Holiday Decorations\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"786\" alt=\"Holiday Decorations\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850289\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-200x83.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-400x165.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-600x248.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-800x331.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations-1200x496.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/holiday-decorations.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-219\"><p>This section is also straight forward. It starts off with a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and then a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/woo-shortcodes-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce Shortcode Element</a> to display the products in one row of three. The parameters for the WooCommerce Shortcode Element are as follows:</p>\n</div>[recent_products limit=\"3\" columns=\"3\" tag=\"holiday-decorations\" orderby=\"rand\" order=\"desc\"]<div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-274{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-274{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-274 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Visual CTA&#8217;s</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-113 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[c32a63588945d1994fe]\" data-title=\"Visual CTA&#8217;s\" title=\"Visual CTA&#8217;s\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"707\" alt=\"Visual CTA&#039;s\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850293\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas-200x74.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas-400x149.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas-600x223.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas-800x298.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas-1200x447.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/visual-ctas.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-220\"><p>Using images as a way to highlight a call-to-action or for advertizing and promotion reasons is standard practice, and the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/avada-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Website Builder</a> makes this task even easier for you. To create this section, a Container Element is added to the page content. To create the style, two 1/2 (50% width) Columns are added to the Container, and each Column then has an image selected as the background overlay. Each Column houses two <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Elements</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and then a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/button-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Button Element</a>. Padding and margin options are set for each Column to create that visual placement.</p>\n<p>The final point to highlight is that each of the two columns is a clickable area by enabling the <strong>Link URL</strong> option within the Column Element settings.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-275{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-275{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-275 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Items For Her</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-114 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[85e279e467884a5f32d]\" data-title=\"Items For Her\" title=\"Items For Her\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"618\" alt=\"Items For Her\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850290\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her-200x65.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her-400x130.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her-600x195.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her-800x260.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her-1200x390.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/items-for-her.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-221\"><p>Because this is a WooCommerce focussed <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">prebuilt website</a>, a third section displaying products has been added to the homepage. It starts off with a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Element</a>, a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/text-block-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Text Block Element</a>, and then a <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/woo-shortcodes-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce Shortcode Element</a> to display the products in a single row of five. The parameters for the WooCommerce Shortcode Element are as follows:</p>\n</div>[recent_products limit=\"5\" columns=\"5\" tag=\"for-her\" orderby=\"rand\" order=\"desc\"]<div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-276{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-276{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-276 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Latest Articles</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-115 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[f5dac9bcebb486b2b65]\" data-title=\"Latest Articles\" title=\"Latest Articles\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"679\" alt=\"Latest Articles\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850291\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles-200x71.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles-400x143.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles-600x214.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles-800x286.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles-1200x429.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/latest-articles.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-222\"><p>Sharing business news via Blog posts is common practice for any website that wants to (a) share promotions and information with their visitors and subscribers, and (B) a healthy way to entice Google to crawl your site for new content. Here you will see the Avada <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/blog-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog Element</a> set to show the three latest blog posts in a <strong>grid layout</strong>. This Element has a wealth of flexible options that will allow you to customize the styling as much as you would like.</p>\n</div></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-60{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-60 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-60{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-60 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-60{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-60 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-body .fusion-flex-container.fusion-builder-row-49{ padding-top : 0px;margin-top : 0px;padding-right : 0px;padding-bottom : 0px;margin-bottom : 0px;padding-left : 0px;}</style></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-50 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start\" style=\"max-width:1352px;margin-left: calc(-4% / 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% / 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-61 fusion-flex-column\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-277{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-277{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-277 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"footer\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">The Footer</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-223\"><p>A website footer aims to help visitors by providing appropriate information and navigation options at the bottom of website pages. Website footer design is underrated and more valuable to your website than you may think and is essential to the overall end-user experience. Three key points stand out, namely:</p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-48\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-thumbs-up fas\" style=\"color:#bc4b20;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">A footer should provide a website visitor with additional choices. If you want people to sign up for your mailing list, view a product demo, or contact you, inviting them at the end of a scroll is a compelling call to action.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-thumbs-up fas\" style=\"color:#bc4b20;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">A footer should create a path for continued engagement by including navigation links to products, services, or other parts of your website.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-thumbs-up fas\" style=\"color:#bc4b20;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">A footer can access essential information like ways to contact your company and customer services, privacy statements, and potential legal disclaimers.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-224\"><p>For the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/handmade/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Handmade</a> prebuilt website, the Footer was created using the Avada <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-footer-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Footer Builder</a> and this particular Footer content and Layout is set to display globally across the website. This means that every page and post will use the same Footer layout without any further conditions set. For example, you can change this if required by creating a unique Footer layout for different pages or posts. Let us take a closer look below:</p>\n</div></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-61{width:100% !important;margin-top : 20px;margin-bottom : 20px;}.fusion-builder-column-61 > .fusion-column-wrapper {padding-top : 0px !important;padding-right : 0px !important;margin-right : 1.92%;padding-bottom : 0px !important;padding-left : 0px !important;margin-left : 1.92%;}@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-61{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-61 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-body .fusion-builder-column-61{width:100% !important;order : 0;}.fusion-builder-column-61 > .fusion-column-wrapper {margin-right : 1.92%;margin-left : 1.92%;}}</style></div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-62 fusion-flex-column\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-278{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-278{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-278 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Footer Subscription Form</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-116 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[009a26f6b8982022f01]\" data-title=\"Footer Subscription Form\" title=\"Footer Subscription Form\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"577\" alt=\"Footer Subscription Form\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-850537\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form-200x61.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form-400x121.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form-600x182.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form-800x243.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form-1200x364.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/footer-subscription-form.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-225\"><p>Different to the <a class=\"fusion-one-page-text-link\" href=\"#subscriptionform\">previous</a> subscription form, this form has been created and then added to the footer to display <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/forms/avada-forms-global-options/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">globally</a> across the website. This is a great way to suggest to your website visitors to subscribe to your business newsletter and hence improve engagement.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\">@media only screen and (max-width:1024px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-279{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:10px!important;margin-left:0px!important;}}@media only screen and (max-width:640px) {.fusion-title.fusion-title-279{margin-top:0px!important; margin-right:0px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important; margin-left:0px!important;}}</style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-279 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\" style=\"font-size:24px;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h4 class=\"title-heading-center\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\">Footer Content</h4></div><div ><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-117 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[45108832e051fb35be8]\" data-title=\"Avada Handmade Footer\" title=\"Avada Handmade Footer\"><img width=\"1900\" height=\"612\" alt=\"Avada Handmade Footer\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-848719\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer-200x64.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer-400x129.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer-600x193.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer-800x258.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer-1200x387.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-handmade-footer.jpg 1900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-226\"><p>The Footer content is divided into two Containers. The first Container has three 1/3 Columns; within are various widgets, <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/title-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Title Elements</a>, <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/social-links-element/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Social Link Elements</a>, a <a href=