n_builder_column fusion-builder-column-65 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-282 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"layouts\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Layouts &amp; Layout Sections</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-229\"><p>Before we look at the specific Layouts on the Avada Restaurant prebuilt website, the first thing to understand is the Layouts and Layout Sections&#8217; architecture. You can think of Layouts as a container for the page content. In contrast, the actual content comes from the various Layout Sections. There are four Layout Sections on a page – the Header, Page Title Bar, Content, and Footer Layout Sections.</p>\n<p>There is a default Global Layout, and any Layout Sections added to that will be shown on all pages of your website. There are Conditional Layouts with conditional logic to determine how the Layout will be used.</p>\n<p>You can make as many Layouts and Layout Sections as you like, and you can use the Layout Sections in multiple Layouts. But you can only use a specific condition on a single Layout, so the theme knows which one to use.</p>\n<p>See <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-layouts-and-layout-sections/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Understanding Layouts &amp; Layout Sections</a> and <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-conditional-layouts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Understanding Conditional Layouts</a> for more info.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-118\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[0d7d46f02f35ad2427a]\" data-title=\"Avada Layouts\" title=\"Avada Layouts\"><img width=\"1989\" height=\"1500\" alt=\"Avada Layouts\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-840348\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-200x151.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-400x302.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-600x452.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-800x603.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example-1200x905.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avadawebsitebuilder-layouts-example.jpg 1989w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-53 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-66 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-283 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"pagesvsposts\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Pages vs. Posts</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-230\"><p>Website pages are allocated for static content such as your website&#8217;s homepage, about, contact page, and so on, and are timeless entities.</p>\n<p>Website posts are allocated to blog content listed in reverse (newest to the oldest) chronological order and are timely. Older posts are archived based on month and year. You can also create content for custom post types or CPT. In Avada, an example of this is the Portfolio post type. Check out this detailed <a href=\"https://wordpress.com/support/post-vs-page/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress article</a> for more information.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-54 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-67 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-284 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"single\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Single Page Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-231\"><p>Let&#8217;s take a look at an Avada Restaurant Single Page Layout, the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/reception-bar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Receptions &amp; Bar</a> page, it is a simple layout and the only addition to the Layout is a Page Title Bar Layout Section.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-119\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[b39723f54c45b9dca9c]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Page Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Page Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"717\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Page Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844896\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout-200x78.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout-400x155.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout-600x233.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout-800x310.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout-1200x465.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-232\"><p>The Conditions are set for this layout to be used on every page, with the exception of the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Homepage</a>, and the two Alternate Home pages, <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/home-alternate-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a> and <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/home-alternate-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/fusion-builder/theme-builder/understanding-conditional-layouts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Conditional Layouts</a> are when you use conditional logic to determine where the Layouts will be used. Without conditions, the Layout would not be used at all. If you mouse over the bottom of a Layout in the edit screen, you will see the Add Conditions link, where you set the conditions for when the layout will be used. See the Layout Conditions dialog below for how the conditions were set.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-120\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[14824a1addb20cf95ab]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Demo &gt; Page Layout Conditions\" title=\"Restaurant Demo &gt; Page Layout Conditions\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"669\" alt=\"Restaurant Demo &gt; Page Layout Conditions\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-704082\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions-200x72.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions-400x145.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions-600x217.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions-800x289.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions-1200x434.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_conditions.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-233\"><p>Now let&#8217;s look at the Page Title Bar Layout Section that was created for the Single Page Layout. In the screenshot below, you can see that it is a very simple layout, with a Separator Element (only visible on large screens) and two Title Elements, displaying a Page Title Bar Subheading and Heading, respectively. There is also a gradient and a background image added to the container.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-121\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[8af16f392081c8d5ed5]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Page Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Page Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"2981\" height=\"1177\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Page Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844894\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls-200x79.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls-400x158.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls-600x237.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls-800x316.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls-1200x474.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_single_page_layout_ptb_ls.jpg 2981w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-234\"><p>Here you can see what the Page Title Bar looks like on the front end on all pages except the Home page and the Alternate Home Pages. At the very top is the Header, with the logo and the menu. Everthing beneath this is coming from the Page Title Bar Layout.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-122\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[b0ef1b79e4a1529d11d]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Demo Custom Page Title Bar Front End\" title=\"Restaurant Demo Custom Page Title Bar Front End\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"463\" alt=\"Restaurant Demo Custom Page Title Bar Front End\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-704121\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end-200x50.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end-400x100.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end-600x150.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end-800x200.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end-1200x300.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_restaurant_page_layout_ptb_front_end.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-55 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-68 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-285 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"404\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">404 Page Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-235\"><p>The next Layout to look at is the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/our-teamm/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">404 page layout</a>. 404 (not found) pages no longer need to be boring and can actually be useful for SEO and to direct your website visitor to alternate resources or a search option. It&#8217;s easy to create a 404 Layout matching the style of your site, and with the content you want.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-123\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[acb970dd09b92c840a5]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; 404 Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; 404 Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"717\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; 404 Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844895\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout-200x78.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout-400x155.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout-600x233.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout-800x310.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout-1200x465.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-236\"><p>If we take a look at this Layout in the Website Builder, we can see it&#8217;s a multi-column layout with various <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/design-elements/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Design Elements</a>, and the Container has both a gradient and a background image set in the Background tab.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-124\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[2d911dc44f1b248e248]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; 404 Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; 404 Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1720\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; 404 Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844893\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls-200x186.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls-400x372.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls-600x558.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls-800x744.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls-1200x1116.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_blog_404_layout_content_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-237\"><p>On the front end, this translates into a clean <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/our-teamm/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">404 page</a>, that very much suits the style of the site, and provides relevant content to a user who has lost their way. As we can see below, the page immediately lets them know the page they are looking for does not exist, and provides a link back to the Homepage.</p>\n<p>Further to this, there is contact information, a helpful menu with common links, and a Search bar. Very nice design, and great functionality! View the live page <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/category/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-125\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[60a2cb57dbfb94a38f3]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Demo 404 Page\" title=\"Restaurant Demo 404 Page\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1048\" alt=\"Restaurant Demo 404 Page\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-704590\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page-200x113.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page-400x227.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page-600x340.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page-800x453.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page-1200x680.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_404_page.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-56 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-69 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-286 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"portfolio\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Single Portfolio Post Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-238\"><p>The next Avada Restaurant layout we are looking at is a Single Portfolio Layout. On this website, portfolio items are used as single dishes, highlighting the individual dine-in Menu items available. Take a look at this <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/menu/kung-pao-chicken/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">example</a>.</p>\n<p>You will see three Layout Sections added to the Page Layout &#8211; a Page Title Bar Layout Section, a Content Layout Section, and a Footer Layout Section, as well as conditions that determine that the Layout will be used on all single portfolio posts. Let&#8217;s look at each of the Layout Sections in the back end, and then look at the result of the Layout on the front end.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-126\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[275c1e423d12fd13065]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"716\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844892\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout-200x77.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout-400x155.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout-600x232.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout-800x310.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout-1200x464.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-287 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Page Title Bar Layout Section</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-239\"><p>The Page Title Bar Layout Section is straightforward. The container has a gradient and a background image, and inside the container are a couple of Separators (with differing Visibility options for large and small screens) and a Title Element that has dynamic content of Portfolio Terms, with a taxonomy of Portfolio Categories. In effect, this simply shows the current Portfolio category in the Page Title Bar.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-127\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[2a99f50bb528398496e]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"808\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844891\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls-200x87.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls-400x175.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls-600x262.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls-800x349.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls-1200x524.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_ptb_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-288 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Content Layout Section</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-240\"><p>The Content Layout Section is also straightforward. There are two columns, one with an Image Element, dynamically pulling the Featured Image of the Portfolio post, and the Content Layout Section Element on the right-hand side, pulling the portfolio post content.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-128\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[80971f73ae09a942b72]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"551\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844890\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls-200x60.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls-400x119.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls-600x179.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls-800x238.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls-1200x357.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_content_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-289 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Footer Layout Section</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-241\"><p>Surprisingly, the Footer Layout Section is the most complex. This is basically a duplicate of the default footer, but made as a Layout Section to enable the addition of three icons highlighting that the restaurant has gluten-free, vegan, and vegetarian options. There are two Containers, one with a gradient and Background image, and a range of design Elements, and a Bottom Container, just with a background color, that is acting as the Copyright Bar in the Layout.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-129\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[1d69803d961505729dc]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Footer Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Footer Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1876\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Portfolio Layout &gt; Footer Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844889\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls-200x203.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls-400x406.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls-600x608.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls-800x811.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls-1200x1217.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_portfolio_layout_footer_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-290 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">The Live Page</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-242\"><p>View the live page <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/takeout/kung-pao-chicken/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. It&#8217;s a stripped-back, clean, and minimalist design, serving as an awesome template for the restaurant&#8217;s menu dishes.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-130\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[d634fe986755b5131c6]\" data-title=\"Avada Restaurant Single Page\" title=\"Avada Restaurant Single Page\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"2455\" alt=\"Avada Restaurant Single Page\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-845623\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page-200x273.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page-400x546.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page-600x818.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page-800x1091.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page-1200x1637.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/avada-restaurant-single-page.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-57 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-70 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-291 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"post\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Single Post Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-243\"><p>Next, we will taker a look at the Single (Blog) Posts Layouts for Avada Restaurant. This Layout has both a Page Title Bar Layout Section and a Content Layout Section. There is no Footer Layout Section added to this Layout, and so it will therefore display the default footer. Take a look at this <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/the-best-table-in-town/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">example</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-131\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[615798e12762781f2c7]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"726\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844888\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout-200x78.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout-400x157.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout-600x235.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout-800x314.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout-1200x471.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-292 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Page Title Bar Layout Section</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-244\"><p>As we can see below, the Page Title Bar Layout Section is again relatively simple. It has both a gradient and a background image on the Container, and inside the Container is a full width column with a separator (with visibility options for just large screens), a H6 Title, pulling the date dynamically from the post, and another two Title Elements (each with different visibility options), pulling the Title dynamically from the Page Title.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-132\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[cb1b4c75e423c1d5632]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout &gt; Page Tile Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout &gt; Page Tile Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"845\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout &gt; Page Tile Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844886\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls-200x91.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls-400x183.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls-600x274.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls-800x365.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls-1200x548.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_ptb_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-293 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Content Layout Section</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-245\"><p>The Content Layout section of the Single Post Layout is a bit more complex. It&#8217;s a multi-Container, multi-Column layout, using a combination of Design Elements, and some <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/layouts/how-to-use-the-avada-layout-elements/https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/layouts/how-to-use-the-avada-layout-elements/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Layout Elements</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-133\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[e0f00026f28b1de6330]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1447\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Single Post Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844885\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls-200x156.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls-400x313.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls-600x469.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls-800x626.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls-1200x939.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_single_post_layout_content_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-294 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">The Live Page</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-246\"><p>View the live page <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/the-best-table-in-town/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. In the Page Title Bar, we can see the date and the Post title, while the Content section has the Featured image and Author Information on the left and the Content Element on the right, followed by Comments and Related Posts Elements below this. At the very bottom is the default site footer.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-134\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[ce8a8067627678e2fde]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Single Post Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Single Post Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"3534\" alt=\"Restaurant Single Post Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-704617\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post-200x382.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post-400x764.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post-600x1146.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post-800x1528.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post-1200x2292.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_single_post.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-f