ayout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Archives Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"728\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Archives Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844884\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls-200x79.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls-400x157.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls-600x236.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls-800x315.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls-1200x472.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_archives_layout_ptb_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-249\"><p>View the live Archive page <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/category/news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. You will see a Page Title Bar that blends in below the header, and displays the Archive Title.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-137\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[47df93b1dd5b65672b8]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Archives page\" title=\"Restaurant Archives page\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1992\" alt=\"Restaurant Archives page\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-727029\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page-200x215.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page-400x431.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page-600x646.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page-800x861.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page-1200x1292.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/6.2.2_restaurant_cal_page.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-59 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-72 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-296 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"woo-pages\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">WooCommerce Pages Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-250\"><p>The next Layout that we will take a look at is the WooCommerce Pages Layout. The conditions on this layout mean that it&#8217;s only used on the three WooCommerce Pages, Cart, Checkout, and My Account. Like the previous Layout, it just adds a Page Title Bar Layout Section.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-138\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[e4bcaf83a9cf03aea47]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Woo Pages Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Woo Pages Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"725\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Woo Pages Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844883\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout-200x78.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout-400x157.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout-600x235.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout-800x314.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout-1200x470.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-251\"><p>The Page Title Bar Layout Section is very simple, and again just adds a gradient and background image to the container, and a Title inside the container.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-139\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[e182f07a8ad43041e9c]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Woo Pages Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Woo Pages Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"730\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Woo Pages Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844877\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls-200x79.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls-400x158.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls-600x237.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls-800x316.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls-1200x474.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_woo_pages_layout_ptb_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-252\"><p>On the front end, here on the My Account Page, we can see the stylish Page Title Bar at the top of the page. It blends seamlessly into the Header thanks to the gradient, and below this, the normal page title is displayed.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-140\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[5cd13f4dfea06b5e63d]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Demo &gt; My Account\" title=\"Restaurant Demo &gt; My Account\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1557\" alt=\"Restaurant Demo &gt; My Account\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-727885\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe-200x168.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe-400x337.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe-600x505.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe-800x673.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe-1200x1010.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/blog_rest_my_account_fe.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-60 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-73 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-297 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"menu-page\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Restaurant Menu Page Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-253\"><p>The penultimate Layout is a Restaurant <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/our-seasonal-menu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Food Menu Page</a> layout, again with only one Layout Section added in the form of a Page Title Bar Layout Section. This is a Conditional layout that is used on just one page, the Our Menu Page.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-141\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[9d1a9cd7724893f16a5]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Restaurant Menu Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Restaurant Menu Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"725\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Restaurant Menu Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844881\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout-200x78.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout-400x157.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout-600x235.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout-800x314.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout-1200x470.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_rest_menu_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-254\"><p>This is a quite interesting Page Title Bar Layout Section. Like the others, there is a gradient and a background image on the Container, this time pulling the Featured Image from the page.</p>\n<p>Inside the Container, there is a Dynamic Title with a Subheading that has a Fallback string of &#8220;BEST TABLE IN TOWN&#8221;, and in the Nested Columns below are another Dynamic Title, this time a H1 pulling the page heading, and on the right hand column, there is a button linking to the new Takeout Menu.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-142\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[194b3c2e8780472c0c9]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Restaurant Menu Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Restaurant Menu Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"1202\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Restaurant Menu Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844897\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls-200x130.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls-400x260.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls-600x390.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls-800x520.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls-1200x780.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_blog_rest_seasonal_menu_page_ptb_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-255\"><p>View the live page <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/our-seasonal-menu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. This restaurant menu page displays the Hors d’oeuvres, Main Menu, and Dessert &amp; Coffee menu items, with 