row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-74 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-298 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"woo-products\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">WooCommerce Single Product Layout</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-256\"><p>Using the <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-woocommerce-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce Builder</a> launched with <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/whats-new-in-7-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada 7.2</a>, you can design and build any type of product page layout that will suit your marketing needs. There are two Layout Sections &#8211; a Single Product Page Title Bar, and a Single Product Content Layout Section, using the Woo Layout Elements. The Conditions on this Layout are set to use this Layout on All WooCommerce Products.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-144\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[4e21c1e40f15ce1dace]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"725\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844882\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout-200x78.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout-400x157.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout-600x235.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout-800x314.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout-1200x470.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-257\"><p>The Page Title Bar Layout Section has a Container with a  gradient and background image, and inside the container are a couple of Separators with different Visibility options for different size screens, plus a Title and a Dynamic Title, pulling Terms, with a taxonomy of product_cat. In effect, this just pulls the product category, and displays it as a title.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-145\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[7592c2ffb2522d8e0d3]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"807\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Page Title Bar Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844880\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls-200x87.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls-400x174.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls-600x262.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls-800x349.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls-1200x523.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_ptb_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-258\"><p>The Content Layout Section has three Containers. The top one displays the Food Category, some Social Sharing Options, and this is also where Woo Notices will appear. The second Container displays the Product Image, price and description, with a dark background color on the second column. And the final container has some Additional Information, and some Related Products below this. For more information about building WooCommerce Product Layouts, see the <a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/documentation/avada/layouts/the-avada-woocommerce-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada WooCommerce Builder</a> documentation.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-146\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[43db5d659d84bc71df1]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"2286\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Content Layout Section\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844879\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls-200x247.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls-400x494.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls-600x741.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls-800x989.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls-1200x1483.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_content_ls.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-299 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">The Live Product Page</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-259\"><p>View the live page <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/restaurant/takeout/ahi-salmon-nigiri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. Viewing the page you will see a Page Tile Bar at the top, which blends seamlessly into the Header thanks to the gradient, and below this, the Content Layout Section displays the product content. This is followed by the default footer.</p>\n</div><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-147\" style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\"><a href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end.jpg\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[56d1dc1e155b6646d5c]\" data-title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Front End\" title=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Front End\"><img width=\"1850\" height=\"2724\" alt=\"Restaurant Prebuilt Website &gt; Product Single Layout &gt; Front End\" src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-844878\" srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end-200x294.jpg 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end-400x589.jpg 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end-600x883.jpg 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end-800x1178.jpg 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end-1200x1767.jpg 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/docs_rest_single_product_layout_front_end.jpg 1850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-62 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-75 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:50px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-300 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-left:0px;\" id=\"conclusion\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Conclusion</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-260\"><p><a href=\"https://bit.ly/35cobDU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Restaurant</a> is modern, stylish, <a href=\"https://avada.theme-fusion.com/website-builder-features/avada-woocommerce-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WooCommerce</a> ready, and available for you to install at the click of a button. Get <a href=\"https://bit.ly/35cobDU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> for WordPress today!</p>\n<p>Hopefully, breaking down these Layouts, and their assigned Layout Sections, gives you a good idea of what&#8217;s possible with the Avada Website Builder. The main benefit of using the Avada Website Builder is that it allows you to create totally unique layouts for your website, and with conditional logic allowing you to specify exactly where that layout will be used.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theme-fusion.com/exploring-the-avada-restaurant-prebuilt-website/\">Exploring The Avada Restaurant Prebuilt Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theme-fusion.com\">ThemeFusion | Avada Website Builder</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://theme-fusion.com/exploring-the-avada-restaurant-prebuilt-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:30:\"https://theme-fusion.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s